https://www.terraform.io/downloads

https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.1.5/terraform_1.1.5_linux_amd64.zip

linux binary download and Unzip it  "Amd64"

1.Download
->wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.1.5/terraform_1.1.5_linux_amd64.zip

2.Unzip it
->unzip terraform_1.1.5_linux_amd64.zip

Archive:  terraform_1.1.5_linux_amd64.zip
  inflating: terraform

3.root@ip-172-31-84-49:~# ls
terraform  terraform_1.1.5_linux_amd64.zip

4.Now, move the terraform binary to the executable directory /usr/local/bin. The executable directory (/usr/local/bin) allows you to run the executable files from anywhere in the Linux system.

sudo mv terraform /usr/local/bin
Finally, verify if terraform has been installed successfully by running the terraform --version command.

terraform -v
Terraform v1.1.5
on linux_amd64


